\pard\f0\fs28  Variable, especially in length of spur; in most plants this is 2-3·5 mm, but in some it is 5-8 mm. The long-spurred variants have been distinguished as{\b  P. azorica} Schlechter,{\i  loc. cit.} (1920) ({\i Habenaria longibracteata} Hochst.), but as variation in other characters shows little correlation and as there is no clear geographical or ecological separation, they are best treated as a variety of {\b 3}.
